Currency Exchange Rate Viewer
Description:
This project uses the National Bank of Poland (NBP) API to provide currency exchange rate information and visualize historical data.

Features:

Fetch current exchange rate for a given currency.
Retrieve and plot historical exchange rate data for a given currency.
Display exchange rates using Matplotlib.

Technologies Used:

Requests library for API calls
Matplotlib for data visualization

Setup Instructions:

1. Install the required packages in bash:
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run the project:
python currency_exchange.py
